This is a copy of the globus-xio package from Globus.  We have one additional patch
to help prevent the code from deadlocking when run in threaded mode.  Instead
of deadlocking, it will now timeout and possibly leak some resources.

See the following Globus JIRA ticket for more details:

http://jira.globus.org/browse/GRAM-229

Source downloaded from 'http://bamboo.globus.org/browse/GT512-RPMCENTOS5-7/artifact/SRPMS/globus-xio-3.0-2.src.rpm'
